@startuml
!theme plain
title 15. CXL Memory Tiering
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "CXL device/pool" as N1 #D6EAF8
rectangle "Fabric manager" as N2 #D5F5E3
rectangle "Coherence warm tier" as N3 #FCF3CF
rectangle "OpenZFS-adjacent roles" as N4 #E8DAEF
rectangle "Scheduler telemetry" as N5 #FADBD8

N1 --> N2 : capacity/latency
N2 --> N3 : ownership epoch
N3 --> N4 : warm placement
N4 --> N5 : qualified media only

note bottom
Actor-facing contract: lower-layer resource identifiers remain hidden unless the ADR explicitly defines them as operator-only evidence.
end note
@enduml
